{"tid":984452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"恐怖夫殺妻睡屍煮頭顱　女兒煮飯驚見殘肢","createTime":"2019-01-16T21:12:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T11:53:01.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"eaa80e7a59c8acf365f2fe0af826ea08d0d151ea","tid":984452,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T21:12:04.000Z","msg":"中國四川驚傳一起恐怖殺妻分屍案，一名54歲金姓男子因感情糾紛，殺死羅姓妻子並分屍，女兒在煮飯時掀開米缸，更驚見羅女被分屍的殘肢。<br />\n據中國微博網友指出，事發在瀘州的「維多利亞領秀」社區，自本月8日起，鄰居就未再見過羅女出門，羅女也沒和家人聯繫。警方獲報後進行調查，證實羅女已在家中遇害。案情指出，金男與羅女發生糾紛後，一怒之下將羅女殺害，更一度伴屍睡覺數日，兩天後將遺體分屍，金男把羅女的頭顱煮熟，把細碎肉塊沖走。周末假日女兒從學校回家，問金男：「媽媽去哪裡了？」金男直呼不知道，說是羅女離家出走。其後女兒煮飯翻開米缸，才驚見媽媽的屍塊，案件因此爆發。<br />\n就有居民在網上留言指出：「我的媽呀！樓下發生分屍案，還要不要我睡覺，電視劇情竟然在我身邊發生。」還有網友指出，金男和羅女是再婚關係，羅女曾是茶樓老闆，目前警方已經著手調查此案，並逮捕金男。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190116/640_36c5fd9d810c1ecc545ae655e0df5858.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190116%2F640_36c5fd9d810c1ecc545ae655e0df5858.jpg&h=4fa81eb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190116/640_986c0b487d7f831eef6074988096fcf3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190116%2F640_986c0b487d7f831eef6074988096fcf3.jpg&h=522c07bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190116/1501721/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190116%2F1501721%2F&d=0%2F9oZcI%2F232Jiv4nLT8%2BtzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=8806d732\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190116%2F1501721%2F&h=d26f420e\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190116/1501721/</a>"},{"pid":"16eadb7c7552bd819586ef415c551e21541536f4","tid":984452,"uid":30708,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T22:15:33.000Z","msg":"媽媽去哪兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59991da114730e82b8371a5f480dc8635d2430df","tid":984452,"uid":6347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T22:18:13.000Z","msg":"到底見到咩先會get到係自己阿媽<br />\n諗下都覺得好恐怖<br />\n如果係我分分鍾以後都唔夠膽開蓋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2eb89034bbd0a452a41dfce8aa18f03fef48ec0","tid":984452,"uid":28624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T22:44:20.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<br />\n個女以後仲點生存呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7838f586f36975918a51f9ee5d8c07598397a209","tid":984452,"uid":71635,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T00:08:48.000Z","msg":"咁兇殘都估到係邊個國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4d2d9a3cb3a74b60c243c752b7546d64f95f70","tid":984452,"uid":92859,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"16eadb7c7552bd819586ef415c551e21541536f4","tid":984452,"uid":30708,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T22:15:33.000Z","msg":"媽媽去哪兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T00:21:50.000Z","msg":"舌尖上的媽媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1215484ce1c62aa9d9d165667e1176d835e6d891","tid":984452,"uid":18948,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T00:32:48.000Z","msg":"好好地蚛蟈地方叫維多利亞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d16fc06ea7ee6e63cb3c6bf12488fbc057de2cd","tid":984452,"uid":200818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T00:37:30.000Z","msg":"唔差在做埋人肉叉燒包啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7abe285b741dae06dd40aa9a791242a3caf2070d","tid":98445